{"tid":1939172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東方: 忠言逆耳 政府剛愎自用 懶理暫停戲院建議終闖禍","createTime":"2020-03-23T03:52:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T09:01:52.000Z","uid":124655,"like":160,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"84b517a53296037603d7b78eddd258501308d705","tid":1939172,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>忠言逆耳 政府剛愎自用 懶理暫停戲院建議終闖禍</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎爆發兩個月時間，行政會議成員<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林正財早在上月9日已經提議</span></strong></span>政府，應就社交距離落實多項針對性措施，例如關閉戲院等娛樂場所的強制措施，但事隔至今一個半月仍然遭政府「冷處理」，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以市民生命「較飛」</span></strong></span>，導致疫情愈趨嚴重，一發不可收拾。<br />\n<br />\n政府專家團之一、香港大學醫學院院長梁卓偉今日（22日）提出關閉食肆及娛樂場所等，避免引致疫情惡化。而林正財上月9日受訪時已表明，強制檢疫14日的措施<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「靠自律一定無用」</span></strong></span>，並認為措施並非滴水不漏。當時他指出，若疫情更壞，可能會減少社交活動，例如關閉戲院、強制公司安排僱員在家工作。<br />\n<br />\n除了林正財外，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始亦曾強烈勸喻，希望戲院、卡拉OK、補習社、興趣小組及會所等多人聚集的場所暫停營業。不過，特首林鄭月娥其後稱，本港是自由社會，故不會強制有關場所暫停營業，相信打開門做生意的商戶都會採取所有確保顧客不受感染的措施；而當時亦已對內地入境人士實施14日強制檢疫措施，減低兩地跨境人流，「封關」建議亦不作考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">疫情至今兩個月，新冠肺炎確診個案有增無減，上周更出現單日確診48宗個案，創疫情爆發以來的新高，而今日亦確診44宗個案，可見政府剛愎自用，未有正視問題所在，漠視市民健康。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d70851308f58f98f70143db2bd707ae4f5f1a4cf","tid":1939172,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da46fad927b569802a9b3822d31364d3b4c7865","tid":1939172,"uid":210463,"like":55,"dislike":13,"score":42,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:58:54.000Z","msg":"咁都要市民去高危場所配合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怪得邊個"},{"pid":"7681315024d7734214d2e673f0dbbad7f87e90c7","tid":1939172,"uid":103615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:59:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"620fb45abfae8c98ce2b7153f6133f8043539937","tid":1939172,"uid":85218,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"quote":{"pid":"2da46fad927b569802a9b3822d31364d3b4c7865","tid":1939172,"uid":210463,"like":55,"dislike":13,"score":42,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:58:54.000Z","msg":"咁都要市民去高危場所配合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怪得邊個"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"岩啊，市民都有責任。但政府既眼界視野唔係應該高D闊Ｄ？"},{"pid":"fb20adf327cf913c06a9d0b3bfbdcfe1e577b8b9","tid":1939172,"uid":124655,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"620fb45abfae8c98ce2b7153f6133f8043539937","tid":1939172,"uid":85218,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"quote":{"pid":"2da46fad927b569802a9b3822d31364d3b4c7865","tid":1939172,"uid":210463,"like":55,"dislike":13,"score":42,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:58:54.000Z","msg":"咁都要市民去高危場所配合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怪得邊個"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"岩啊，市民都有責任。但政府既眼界視野唔係應該高D闊Ｄ？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T04:03:47.000Z","msg":"林奠直頭冇遠見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3164a98bc43b5ae1f15dc2734338b721abb1bd9b","tid":1939172,"uid":169195,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"84b517a53296037603d7b78eddd258501308d705","tid":1939172,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>忠言逆耳 政府剛愎自用 懶理暫停戲院建議終闖禍</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎爆發兩個月時間，行政會議成員<spa